<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٤٨٤ - عَنْ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ كَثِيرٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ شُعْبَةَ بْنِ الْحَجَّاجِ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ الْحَكَمَ بْنَ عُتَيْبَةَ، وَحَمَّادًا عَنْ ذَلِكَ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ الْحَكَمُ:</span> <span class="c2">«يُعِيدُ»</span>،<span class="c5"> وَحَمَّادٌ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا يُعِيدُ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>